OL,3,CPolice officer who shot man thought to
OL,4,Cbe a terrorist speaks for first time
OL,6,FJean Charles de Menezes was shot seven
OL,7,Ftimes by police officers - one of them
OL,8,Fhas spoken publicly for the first time
OL,10,FA Met police officer who shot an
OL,11,Finnocent man wrongly suspected of
OL,12,Fbeing a terrorist after the 7/7 London
OL,13,Fbombings has spoken for the first
OL,14,Ftime, saying he believed "we were
OL,15,Fgoing to die" if he didn't act.
OL,17,FJean Charles de Menezes, a 27-year-old
OL,18,FBrazilian electrician, was killed a
OL,19,Ffortnight after suicide bombers
OL,20,Ftargeted three Tube lines and a London
OL,21,Fbus on July 7 2005, killing 52 people.
