OL,3,CPolice officer who shot man thought to
OL,4,Cbe a terrorist speaks for first time
OL,6,FNow the firearms officer, who has
OL,7,Fremained anonymous for nearly 20
OL,8,Fyears, defended the shooting for the
OL,9,Ffirst time as part of Channel 4's
OL,10,FShoot To Kill: Terror On The Tube
OL,11,Fdocumentary.
OL,13,F"Reliving it in this detail is
OL,14,Fpainful," the officer only known as
OL,15,FC12 said.
OL,17,FMr de Menezes lived in an apartment
OL,18,Fblock linked to one of the suspects
OL,19,Finvolved in a failed attempt to target
OL,20,FLondon's transport network on 21 July.
