OL,3,CPolice officer who shot man thought to
OL,4,Cbe a terrorist speaks for first time
OL,6,FThe next day, police followed him onto
OL,7,Fa train at Stockwell Tube station in
OL,8,Fsouth London, where he was shot seven
OL,9,Ftimes by two officers.
OL,11,FTwo days later on July 23, Scotland
OL,12,FYard confirmed Mr de Menezes was not
OL,13,Fconnected to the July 21 attacks.
OL,15,FThe officer said: "I want to make sure
OL,16,Fthat people understand these
OL,17,Fdecisions, although they're taken
OL,18,Fquickly, they're not taken lightly.
