OL,6,F"I remember the surveillance officer
OL,7,Fthen in full body contact with him,
OL,8,Fand apparently what he was trying to
OL,9,Fdo was pin his hands so that he
OL,10,Fcouldn't detonate.
OL,12,F"I'm expecting an explosion at any
OL,13,Fmoment, he's gonna blow. We're gonna
OL,14,Fdie. But that's the nub of it.
OL,16,F"If I don't do something now, we are
OL,17,Fall going to die."
