OL,3,CPolice officer who shot man thought to
OL,4,Cbe a terrorist speaks for first time
OL,6,FDame Cressida Dick, who was promoted
OL,7,Fto Metropolitan Police commissioner in
OL,8,F2017, led the operation in which Mr de
OL,9,FMenezes died.
OL,11,FA jury cleared her of any blame in his
OL,12,Fdeath, but the Met Police was fined
OL,13,F#175,000 and ordered to pay #385,000
OL,14,Fin costs after being found guilty of
OL,15,Fendangering the public.
OL,17,FShoot To Kill: Terror On The Tube will
OL,18,Fair on November 10 and 11 on Channel 4.
